text: The 1909–10 Kentucky State Wildcats men's basketball team competed on behalf of the University of Kentucky during the 1909-1910 season. The head coach was Edwin R. Sweetland, and the team finished with a final record of 4-8. ==Schedule== |- !colspan=12 style="background:#273BE2; color:white;"| Regular Season ==References== Kentucky Category:Kentucky Wildcats men's basketball seasons
